name: Diagnosis Type SnCT
description: A code from the SNOMED Clinical Terminology UK coding system that describes a diagnosis. Any code from the SNOMED CT UK 'Diagnosis' subset with subset original id 1261000000136; the corresponding SNOMED CT UK Refset fully specified name is 'Diagnosis simple reference set (foundation metadata concept)' with Refset Id 999000711000000101.
